invalid type: string "Join Behaviour\nINNER JOIN Only rows with matching values in both tables.\nLEFT (OUTER) JOIN All rows from the left table, plus matches from the right (NULL where no match).\nRIGHT (OUTER) JOINAll rows from the right table, plus matches from the left (NULL where no match).\nFULL (OUTER) JOIN All rows from both tables; unmatched sides filled with NULL.\n\nPartially\nCommittedº